attributes.description: The "TYCHON Endpoint Browser" dashboard provides host visualization data for a single endpoint at a time. The dashboard is a set of several individual views broken down by tabs near the top of the screen. The TYCHON Endpoint Browser - Benchmark Results view displays all Benchmark SCAP scan results for the OS and Software installed.
